<%= provide(:body_id, 'index') %>
<%= provide(:result, '工单查看') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>代理商工单查看</h1>

        <p>
          工单列表根据出口对各个测试网站的评分进行统计，主要统计负分、总分两项指标。<br/>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li>
          <a href="/">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
            首页
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/workorders">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
            工单查看
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
          查看出口周报表
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="row-fluid hidden-desktop hidden-phone">
        <div class="span12">
          <h4 class="title">[<%= @dls_name %>] 所辖出口得分排名表如下示：</h4>

          <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
          <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-radmin">
            <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="text-align:center;">日期</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">内容</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">动作</th>
              <th style="text-align:center;">查看日期</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <% @out_arr.each_with_index do |line, i| %>
              <tr>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <%= line[0].strftime('%Y年-%m月%d日') %> - <%= line[1].strftime('%Y年-%m月%d日') %>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;"><%= line[2] %></td>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <a class="btn btn-small btn-info" href="<%= week_wo_workorders_path(date: line[0]) %>">
                    <i class="icon-edit icon-white"></i>
                    查看
                  </a>
                </td>
                <td style="text-align:center;">
                  <% unless line[3].blank? %>
                    <%= line[3].strftime('%Y年-%m月%d日 %H:%M:%S') %>
                  <% end %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p></p>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          Etiam varius erat in nisl egestas id auctor lacus consectetur.
          Ut dui risus, auctor a malesuada volutpat, tempus sit amet arcu.
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">Jane Doe via Mobile</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>